# X4 toolkit path configuration — copy to ".claude/x4-paths.env" (gitignored) and edit.
#
# This is the single, cross-platform source of truth for where everything lives. The hooks
# and the bin/ scripts source this file. EVERY path is overridable — nothing is hardcoded to
# one OS or one user. Leave a key blank/absent if it doesn't apply to you.
#
# The install scripts (install.sh / install.ps1) write this file for you; edit by hand if you
# prefer. On Windows you may use either C:\... or /c/... (Git Bash) style — the hooks
# normalize both. Quote values that contain spaces.

# --- the toolkit itself (usually auto-detected as the repo/project root) ---
# X4_TOOLKIT="/home/you/x4-claude-toolkit"

# --- the game install (folder holding 01.cat..09.cat and extensions/ego_dlc_*) ---
# Linux (Steam):   X4_GAME="$HOME/.steam/steam/steamapps/common/X4 Foundations"
# Linux (extra library): X4_GAME="/path/to/SteamLibrary/steamapps/common/X4 Foundations"
# Windows:         X4_GAME="C:/Program Files (x86)/Steam/steamapps/common/X4 Foundations"
# macOS:           X4_GAME="$HOME/Library/Application Support/Steam/steamapps/common/X4 Foundations"
X4_GAME=""

# --- read-only unpacked base game (default: $X4_TOOLKIT/reference) ---
# X4_REFERENCE="$X4_TOOLKIT/reference"

# --- active user profile (saves, config.xml, debug log, active content.xml) ---
# Linux:   X4_PROFILE="$HOME/.config/EgoSoft/X4/<id>"   (or your custom location)
# Windows: X4_PROFILE="$USERPROFILE/Documents/Egosoft/X4/<id>"
X4_PROFILE=""

# --- debug log (X4 names it debug.txt by default; some setups use debuglog.log) ---
# X4_DEBUGLOG="$X4_PROFILE/debug.txt"

# --- where your mod source repos live (one folder per mod) ---
# X4_MODS="$X4_TOOLKIT/mods"

# --- live deploy target the game reads extensions from (for the test loop) ---
# Usually inside the game dir; some setups symlink it elsewhere.
# X4_EXTENSIONS="$X4_GAME/extensions"

# --- XRCatTool (Egosoft; you supply it). Used via bin/xrcat (wine on Linux/macOS). ---
# XRCATTOOL="$X4_TOOLKIT/tools/XRCatTool/XRCatTool.exe"

# --- Steam app manifest (for the stale-reference check; auto-derived from X4_GAME if unset) ---
# X4_APPMANIFEST="/path/to/steamapps/appmanifest_392160.acf"

# --- optional: your OWN free Nexus API key for x4modlist (never commit a real key) ---
# X4_NEXUS_KEY=""
